INSERT INTO `news` VALUES ('1', '乌托邦官方助手', '广州软件学院2022虎年新春献词', '27', '2022/3/13 18:41:28', '1', '<p><br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 24pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">金牛奋蹄开锦绣，</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">玉虎</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">迎春露新颜</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">。</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">在这辞旧迎新的欢庆时刻，我谨代表</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">学校</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">董事会，向关心支持</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">学校</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">发展的各级领导、各界朋友，向</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">为学校建设作出贡献的</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">全体师生员工，向心系母校发展的各届校友，致以节日的问候和新年的祝福！</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 24pt;\"><br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\"><img class=\"lazy img-responsive\" src=\"https://news.seig.edu.cn/Uploads/2022-02-18/620efa0d04b42.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; display: inline-block; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"><br></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 24pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">2021年是广州软件学院转设为独立建制的应用型本科高校的元年，学校</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">紧密</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">围绕“规范达标、品牌提升”双计划，</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">在严格做好</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">疫情防控</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">工作的基础上</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">，</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">教育教学工作井然有序，专业建设和科研创新工作取得突破，办学内涵不断提升；学生工作、校园文化建设亮点纷呈，人才培养成效显著。回首2021年，所有成绩的取得，离不开全体教职工的积极进取和努力贡献，更离不开各界朋友和校友的大力支持，借此机会，向大家表示诚挚的感谢！</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\"></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 24pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">虎踞龙盘今胜昔，如虎添翼迎华章。展望2022年，广州软件学院将迎来建校20周年，《广州软件学院“十四五”发展规划》正式实施。站在崭新的历史起点，我愿与大家一道，扬起勤奋的风帆，荡起创新的双桨，迎着和沐的春风，启航新的征程，共创属于广软新的更大辉煌！</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\"></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 24pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">最后，祝福大家身体健康，家庭美满，事业有成，虎年大吉！</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\"></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 24pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\"></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"right\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 24pt; text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">广州软件学院</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">董事长&nbsp;梁冠军</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\"></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"right\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 24pt; text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">于壬寅新春</span></p>', 'VIP', '金牛奋蹄开锦绣，玉虎迎春露新颜。在这辞旧迎新的欢庆时刻，我谨代表学校董事会，向关心支持学校发展的各级领导、各界朋友，向为学校建设作出贡献的全体师生员工，向心系母校发展的各届校友，致以节日的问候和新年的祝福！', 'http://localhost:3000/uploads/1.jpg', '0', '0', '0');
INSERT INTO `news` VALUES ('2', '乌托邦官方助手', '学校领导巡查“开学第一课”（图文）', '10', '2022/3/5 14:23:52', '0', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 24.1pt;\"><b style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">本网讯</span></b><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp;2</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">月</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">28</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">日，广软师生迎来了新学期的“开学第一课”。</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">校长</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">张强、党委书记</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">兼督导专员</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">刘友坤、副</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">校长徐祥</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">、</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">副校长袁志、校长助理张广金</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">分为两组深入教学区巡查教学情况。</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">校长</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">办公室、党委宣传部、教务处、各系（部）负责人、教学督导等也分别到E型教学楼、实验大楼S区、T区、U区、2号实验楼进行课堂教学情况检查。</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 255); font-size: 12pt;\"></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; line-height: 24p