t;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; color: rgb(0, 0, 255); font-size: 12pt;\">迟云平常务副校长</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; color: rgb(0, 0, 255); font-size: 12pt;\">走访慰问教职工</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; color: rgb(0, 0, 255); font-size: 12pt;\"></span></p><p class=\"p\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: -11.35pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; color: rgb(0, 0, 255); font-size: 12pt;\"></span></p><p class=\"p\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: -11.35pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; color: rgb(0, 0, 255); font-size: 12pt;\"><img class=\"lazy img-responsive\" src=\"https://news.seig.edu.cn/Uploads/2022-02-23/62160473a7fe7.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; display: inline-block; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"><br></span></p><p class=\"p\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: -11.35pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; color: rgb(0, 0, 255); font-size: 12pt;\">徐祥副校长走访</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; color: rgb(0, 0, 255); font-size: 12pt;\">慰问教职工</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; color: rgb(0, 0, 255); font-size: 12pt;\"></span></p><p class=\"p\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: -11.35pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; color: rgb(0, 0, 255); font-size: 12pt;\"></span></p><p class=\"p\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: -11.35pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; color: rgb(0, 0, 255); font-size: 12pt;\"><img class=\"lazy img-responsive\" src=\"https://news.seig.edu.cn/Uploads/2022-02-23/6216047fe1e26.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; display: inline-block; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"><br></span></p><p class=\"p\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: -11.35pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; color: rgb(0, 0, 255); font-size: 12pt;\">袁志副校长走访慰问教职工</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; color: rgb(0, 0, 255); font-size: 12pt;\"></span></p><p class=\"p\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: -11.35pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; color: rgb(0, 0, 255); font-size: 12pt;\"></span></p><p class=\"p\" align=\"justify\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: -11.35pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 24.1pt; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">学</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">校领导与教职工亲切交谈</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">，</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">给大家带去美好的新春祝愿和真挚问候</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">。</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">校领导详细询问了各职能部门和</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">教学系部</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">春季学期开学准备工作和新学期教学计划等情况</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">，</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">并鼓励老师们继续发扬优良作风</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">，</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">以饱满的工作状态和昂扬的精神面貌做好新学期各项工作</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">，</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">再接再厉</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">、</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">开拓创新</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">，</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">在各自的岗位上取得优异成绩</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">。</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">同时</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">，</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">学校领导也要求各部门和教职员工严格</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">遵照</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">上级要求和学校规定</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">，</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">树立</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">“</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">个人是自己健康第一责任人意识</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">”，</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">扎实做好疫情防控相关工作</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">。</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\"></span></p><p class=\"p\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: -11.35pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 24.1pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">教职工</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">感谢学校领导的问候和祝福，</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">并</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">纷纷表示，将</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">根据学校要求</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">处理好疫情防控与工作之间的关系，以全新的姿态投入到工作中去，以更大的努力推进规范达标和品牌提升，以更大的干劲推动学校各项事业的发展。</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\"></span></p><p class=\"p\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: -11.35pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 24.1pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">根据</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">学校</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">安排，学生于2月</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">26</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">日、</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">27</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">日分期分批错峰有序返校，并注册领取教材，</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">2</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">月</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">28</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">日正式上课。</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 21px; font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 21px; font-size: 10.5pt;\"></span></p><p class=\"p\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: -11.35pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 24pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\"></span></p><p class=\"p\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: -11.35pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 24pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 12pt;\">（供稿：党委宣传部&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 12pt;\">摄影：</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 12pt;\">林延军、胡争、杨洋、</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 12pt;\">贺芋婷&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;编辑、初审</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 12pt;\">：房小铃&nbsp;复审：林延军 &nbsp;终审：胡争）&nbsp;</span></p>', 'VIP', '', null, '0', '0', '2');
INSERT INTO `news` VALUES ('15', '乌托邦官方助手', '【视频】第十二届校园文化艺术节开幕式暨2021年迎新晚会', '1', '2022/3/5 14:23:52', '0', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; text-indent: 24.1pt;\"><b style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体;\">本网讯</span></b><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体;\">“广州软件学院谭医生，您好。我中心发现贵校有一名学生是一位确诊病例的密接者，姓名是李某……上午在某某餐厅就餐，与该新冠病毒核酸检测为阳性的确诊病例同时间在餐厅就餐。请学校立刻配合疾控中心做好新冠肺炎疫情防控应急工作……”，为切实做好学校春季开学疫情防控工作，2月25日下午，我校组织开展2022年春季学期开学新冠肺炎疫情防控应急处置演练。学校党委书记兼督导专员刘友坤担任总指挥，电子系和软件系承办此次演练工作。学校新冠肺炎疫情防控专班成员及相关部门负责人、各系党总支书记、老师代表观摩了演练。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体;\"></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 24px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312; color: blue;\"><img class=\"lazy img-responsive\" src=\"https://news.seig.edu.cn/Uploads/2022-02-25/6218e3fe83d6a.JPG\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; display: inline-block; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"><br></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 24px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312; color: blue;\">模拟将密接学生通过120救护车转运到属地医疗机构</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; text-indent: 24pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体;\">演练的方式是实战演练，主要检验学校应急响应、指挥调度、现场组织等突发处置能力。演练现场，包括安保人员、校医室医生、社区三人组、学生代表、防疫专班代表、辅导员、模拟地方医疗机构等在内的参演队伍，模拟了课室区出现密切接触者的情形，动作、场景、旁白、对白加以融合，衔接自然，一幕幕推进实施演练。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 24px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312; color: blue;\"><img class=\"lazy img-responsive\" src=\"https://news.seig.edu.cn/Uploads/2022-02-25/6218e40fd8009.JPG\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; display: inline-block; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 24px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312; color: blue;\">学校模拟召开会议，启动学校新冠肺炎疫情防控处置应急预案</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 24px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312; color: blue;\"></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; text-indent: 24pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体;\">接到校医报告学生系密切接触者，学校新冠肺炎疫情防控应急工作领导小组立即按照《广州市学校防控新冠肺炎疫情应急处置预案（试行）》要求，启动学校新冠肺炎疫情防控处置应急预案，召开会议组织学校疫情防控各小组按照工作职责启动响应工作。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 24px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312; color: blue;\"><img class=\"lazy img-responsive\" src=\"https://news.seig.edu.cn/Uploads/2022-02-25/6218e423a6ba7.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; display: inline-block; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"><br></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 24px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312; color: blue;\">组织管控对象转运隔离</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; text-indent: 24pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体;\">学校启动应急处置预案后，学校通知各班级取消聚集性活动，涉疫教学楼、宿舍楼学生佩戴医用外科口罩或以上防护级别口罩。在教学楼和宿舍楼等待进一步处置，校园实施封闭管控，人员不得外出，对涉疫场所进行消杀。学校配合疾控机构落实各场所终末消毒工作，按照疾控部门的意见及要求对校园进行封闭封控管理，开展全员核酸筛查，做好家校沟通，落实线上教学及师生心理疏导、引导舆情、后续核酸检测工作等。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 24px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312; color: blue;\"><img class=\"lazy img-responsive\" src=\"https://news.seig.edu.cn/Uploads/2022-02-25/6218e44c97cac.JPG\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; display: inline-block; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"><br></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 24px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312; color: blue;\">疾控机构对涉疫场所进行终末消毒</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体;\"></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; text-indent: 24pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体;\">学校党委书记刘友坤在总结讲评指出，演练严格按照当前疫情防控常态化工作要求，能及时对密切接触者按流程处置、人员排查、场所消杀、核酸检测等应急处置环节进行场景模拟，疫情演练的目的是熟悉流程，发现问题，增强各部门应急处置能力，促进疫情防控工作的程序化、规范化。他要求学校各级领导干部在思想上要高度重视疫情防控工作，做好学生返校前后的信息摸查工作，配合相关部门进行流调，随时准备启动应急预案，有序推进平安校园建设。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><img class=\"lazy img-responsive\" src=\"https://news.seig.edu.cn/Uploads/2022-02-25/6218e459dd414.JPG\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; display: inline-block; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 24px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312; color: blue;\">学校党委书记刘友坤总结讲评</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; text-indent: 24pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体;\">另外，2月23日、24日，<span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">从化区卫健局、卫生监督所和</span>从化区教育局疫情防控督导组分别到我校检查学校开学防疫工作。刘友坤书记就学校校园疫情防控工作的组织机构、物资保障、寒假疫情防控工作和2022年春季学期师生返校疫情防控准备工作安排作了汇报。检查组一行<span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">实地查看了学生食堂、医务室、临时隔离区、健康观察室等场所，</span>认真查阅了我校疫情防控的制度建设、校园出入管理、防疫物资储备、疫情防控台账资料等，充分肯定当前学校疫情防控工作，并对下一步加强和完善疫情防控提出了指导意见。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 24px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312; color: blue;\"></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 24px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312; color: blue;\"><img class=\"lazy img-responsive\" src=\"https://news.seig.edu.cn/Uploads/2022-02-25/6218e4695f228.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; display: inline-block; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"><br></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 24px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312; color: blue;\">从化区卫健局检查组到校检查我校疫情防控工作</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 24px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312; color: blue;\"><img class=\"lazy img-responsive\" src=\"https://news.seig.edu.cn/Uploads/2022-02-25/6218e47bf04c2.JPG\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; display: inline-block; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"><br></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 24px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312; color: blue;\">从化区教育局疫情防控督导组到我校检查疫情防控工作</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; （供稿：党委宣传部</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 12pt;\">编辑：贺芋婷</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 12pt;\">复审：房小铃</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 12pt;\">终审：林延军）</span></p>', 'VIP', '', null, '0', '0', '2');
INSERT INTO `news` VALUES ('16', '乌托邦官方助手', '【学习强国】发挥专业所长 让校园建筑的魅力跃然纸上（2022年3月1日）', '6', '2022/3/5 14:23:52', '0', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 24pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">金牛奋蹄开锦绣，</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">玉虎</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">迎春露新颜</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">。</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">在这辞旧迎新的欢庆时刻，我谨代表</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">学校</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">董事会，向关心支持</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">学校</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">发展的各级领导、各界朋友，向</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">为学校建设作出贡献的</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">全体师生员工，向心系母校发展的各届校友，致以节日的问候和新年的祝福！</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 24pt;\"><br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\"><img class=\"lazy img-responsive\" src=\"https://news.seig.edu.cn/Uploads/2022-02-18/620efa0d04b42.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; display: inline-block; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"><br></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 24pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">2021年是广州软件学院转设为独立建制的应用型本科高校的元年，学校</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">紧密</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">围绕“规范达标、品牌提升”双计划，</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">在严格做好</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">疫情防控</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">工作的基础上</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">，</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">教育教学工作井然有序，专业建设和科研创新工作取得突破，办学内涵不断提升；学生工作、校园文化建设亮点纷呈，人才培养成效显著。回首2021年，所有成绩的取得，离不开全体教职工的积极进取和努力贡献，更离不开各界朋友和校友的大力支持，借此机会，向大家表示诚挚的感谢！</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\"></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 24pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">虎踞龙盘今胜昔，如虎添翼迎华章。展望2022年，广州软件学院将迎来建校20周年，《广州软件学院“十四五”发展规划》正式实施。站在崭新的历史起点，我愿与大家一道，扬起勤奋的风帆，荡起创新的双桨，迎着和沐的春风，启航新的征程，共创属于广软新的更大辉煌！</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\"></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 24pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">最后，祝福大家身体健康，家庭美满，事业有成，虎年大吉！</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\"></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 24pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\"></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"right\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 24pt; text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">广州软件学院</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">董事长&nbsp;梁冠军</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\"></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"right\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 24pt; text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">于壬寅新春</span></p>', 'VIP', '', null, '0', '0', '3');
INSERT INTO `news` VALUES ('17', '乌托邦官方助手', '【媒体聚焦】粤高校毕业生供需见面活动(从化专场)在广软举办受媒体关注', '0', '2022/3/5 14:23:52', '0', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 24.1pt;\"><b style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">本网讯</span></b><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp;2</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">月</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">28</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">日，广软师生迎来了新学期的“开学第一课”。</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">校长</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">张强、党委书记</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">兼督导专员</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">刘友坤、副</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">校长徐祥</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">、</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">副校长袁志、校长助理张广金</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">分为两组深入教学区巡查教学情况。</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">校长</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">办公室、党委宣传部、教务处、各系（部）负责人、教学督导等也分别到E型教学楼、实验大楼S区、T区、U区、2号实验楼进行课堂教学情况检查。</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 255); font-size: 12pt;\"></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312;