/span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 255); font-size: 12pt;\"><img class=\"lazy img-responsive\" src=\"https://news.seig.edu.cn/Uploads/2022-02-28/621c75a928770.JPG\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; display: inline-block; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"><br></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 255); font-size: 12pt;\">学校领导巡查智慧教室</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 255); font-size: 12pt;\"></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 255); font-size: 12pt;\"><img class=\"lazy img-responsive\" src=\"https://news.seig.edu.cn/Uploads/2022-02-28/621c75556a7c1.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; display: inline-block; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"><br></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 255); font-size: 12pt;\">学生意气风发地行走在校园</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 24pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">2021</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">—</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">2022学年第二学期全校共开设课程679门，其中必修课421门，选修课258多门（含19门智慧树在线课）。为了不影响教学秩序，学</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">校</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">领导、各系（部）负责人、教学督导及教务处工作人员主要在课室外或教室门口附近巡查，并认真检查防疫物资配备情况。从检查情况来看，学生到课情况良好，精神饱满；任课教师认真上课，教学秩序良好，防疫物资及防控措施按要求落实。</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\"></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\"></span></p><p class=\"p\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: -11.3pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 24pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 12pt;\">（</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 12pt;\">供稿：党委宣传部</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 12pt;\">摄影：</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 12pt;\">房小铃、</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 12pt;\">朱健乐、朱苑菁</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp;编辑、初审：房小铃&nbsp;复审：贺芋婷 终审：林延军&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 12pt;\">）</span></p>', 'VIP', '', null, '0', '0', '3');
INSERT INTO `news` VALUES ('18', '乌托邦官方助手', '【人民日报】广东省弦歌教育学会成立（2021年12月1日）', '0', '2022/3/5 14:23:52', '0', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 24.1pt;\"><b style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">本网讯</span></b><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp;2月24日下午，我校召开2022年春季学期中层干部大会，校长张强</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">、</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">党委书记兼督导专员刘友坤、执行董事兼常务副校长迟云平、</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">副校长徐祥、副校长袁志、副董事长助理叶倩</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">如、全体中层干部和助理出席会议。会议由执行董事兼常务副校长迟云平主持。</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255); font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 255); font-size: 12pt;\"><img class=\"lazy img-responsive\" src=\"https://news.seig.edu.cn/Uploads/2022-02-25/621891f952089.JPG\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; display: inline-block; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"><br></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 255); font-size: 12pt;\">迟云平常务副校长主持</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 255); font-size: 12pt;\">大会</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 255); font-size: 12pt;\"></span></p><p class=\"15\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 24pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">刘友坤书记传达了上级相关会议精神、</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">疫情防控工作要求，并介绍我校2022年春季学期师生返校疫情防控工作情况，要求学校各级领导干部对疫情防控工作不能放松，要严格落实疫情防控工作责任，既要做好新冠肺炎疫情的防控，也要提醒师生员工做好其它流行性传染病的预防。</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">他还通报了新学期学校</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">党建</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">重点工作任务：</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">建立学校党史学习教育常态化机制，强化基层党组织的政治职能，提升基层党组织的生机活力，持续加强党建品牌建设，维护学校意识形态和政治安全，落实学校疫情防控措施，确保校园安全稳定。</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255); font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 255); font-size: 12pt;\"><img class=\"lazy img-responsive\" src=\"https://news.seig.edu.cn/Uploads/2022-02-25/6218920486631.JPG\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; display: inline-block; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"><br></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 255); font-size: 12pt;\">刘友坤书记讲话</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 255); font-size: 12pt;\"></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 24pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">张强校长总结了过去一年学校的工作情况，并就学校2022年重点推进的工作进行部署。张强认为，过去一年是广软元年，学校内涵建设取得突破，校企合作扎实推进，人才培养成绩喜人，办学条件逐步改善，为今后学校各项工作打下了基础。张强指出</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">，</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">过去</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">一年</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">取得</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">的</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">成绩来之不易，应当好好珍惜,虽然工作初见成效，但还需加倍努力。他结合今年学校发展面临的特殊形势和工作的基本要求，分析了当前工作存在的不足，提出了下一步工作的思考。</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255); font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 255); font-size: 12pt;\"><img class=\"lazy img-responsive\" src=\"https://news.seig.edu.cn/Uploads/2022-02-25/6218920fbd3cd.JPG\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; display: inline-block; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"><br></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 255); font-size: 12pt;\">张强校长讲话</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 255); font-size: 12pt;\"></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 24pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">张强强调，学校将沿着“聚焦复评 任务导向 营造氛围 突出实效 ”的思路，致力改善办学条件、提升办学品质、充实师资队伍、深化校企合作、拓展办学资源、完善内部管理，</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">他要求全体中层干部强化责任、扩宽视野、带好队伍、善做善成</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">，带领全校师生</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">以饱满的工作状态和优异的工作成绩通过学校转设复评，并着眼做好</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">合格评估</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">，努力营造良好的氛围庆祝建校二十周年，以实际行动和优异成绩迎接党的二十大的胜利召开。</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\"></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 24pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; line-height: 24px; font-size: 12pt;\">（供稿：党委宣传部&nbsp;贺芋婷&nbsp;摄影：林延军&nbsp;编辑：房小铃&nbsp;复审：林延军&nbsp;终审：胡争）</span></p>', 'VIP', '', null, '0', '0', '3');
INSERT INTO `news` VALUES ('19', '乌托邦官方助手', '【南方日报】汇聚侨心侨力 实现伟大复兴（2021年11月19日）', '0', '2022/3/5 14:23:52', '0', '<p class=\"p\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: -11.35pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 24.1pt;\"><b style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">本网讯</span></b><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">2月2</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">3</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">日</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">是学校教职工返校上班的第一天，校长</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">张强、党委</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">书记</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">兼督导专员</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">刘友坤</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">、执行董事兼常务</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">副校长</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">迟云平</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">、</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">副</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">校长</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">徐祥、副</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">校长袁志、副董事长助理叶倩如、校长助理张广金等领导深入各系部看望教职工、实地检查开学准</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">备工作</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">的</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">情况。</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; color: rgb(0, 0, 255); font-size: 12pt;\"></span></p><p class=\"p\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: -11.35pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neu